            <description><![CDATA[实现烤肠自由了！！ <br> <br>【38.9】美享时刻 火山石奥尔良烤肠*30根 <br> <br>算下来一根才一块多，线下一根都要5大洋了吧，有空气炸锅的就可以简单操作啦，解冻后用小刀划一下在空气炸锅里200°15分钟就能开吃，一口咬下去炒鸡美味肉的质感很扎实，吃着超满足的！！ <img style src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gz7gwyct7hj20j60j60v0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gz7gwz039sj20j60j6go4.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gz7gwzkkq4j20j60j6abk.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gz7gx02psnj20j60o5jtl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gz7gx0op0jj20j60nl40k.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1gz7gx163q5j20j60o2di2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
